533
00:30:50.860 --> 00:30:51.860
WE’RE HERE.

534
00:30:51.860 --> 00:30:52.860
WE’RE QUEER.

535
00:30:52.860 --> 00:30:56.179
(Except if we’re causing a fuss, we don’t
