542
00:31:21.280 --> 00:31:25.490
Feeling that alone and isolated is a huge
contributing factor for anxiety and depression

543
00:31:25.490 --> 00:31:28.150
among queer youth, and adults too.

544
00:31:28.150 --> 00:31:33.030
Having media to supplement what is missing
in real life is the best way for people to

545
00:31:33.030 --> 00:31:34.679
see shared experiences.

546
00:31:34.679 --> 00:31:38.900
But those messages aren’t going to come
across the way they need to if these experiences

547
00:31:38.900 --> 00:31:44.299
are removed from identifiable queer characters,
and then appropreated into media depicting

548
00:31:44.299 --> 00:31:45.640
straight people.

549
00:31:45.640 --> 00:31:50.240
And when it comes to separating our identities
from our experiences, that isn’t even the

