556
00:32:13.740 --> 00:32:17.779
for queer people who are trying to figure
out how to fit into the world.

557
00:32:17.779 --> 00:32:21.799
And it’s bad for straight and cis people
who are trying to relate to us, and becoming

558
00:32:21.799 --> 00:32:25.570
frustrated that we aren’t like how we are
in the media they watch.

559
00:32:25.570 --> 00:32:30.179
Somehow, we went from fighting to tell our
stories, to setting up media producers as

560
00:32:30.179 --> 00:32:32.559
